        <content>&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;The PowerPoint presentation you will see next discusses the key strategies and how they are applied in practice. Before you watch, note some of your own thoughts about the strategies. If you took the &lt;a title="Self-Assessment" href="http://lincs.ed.gov/programs/teachereffectiveness/self-assessment" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adult Education Teacher Competencies Self-Assessment&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, look at your assessment priorities. (If you wish, jot your answers to the questions in your &lt;a target="_blank" href="$@JOURNALVIEWBYID*4993@$"&gt;journal&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
