        <title>Slide Viewing Activity</title>
        <content>&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;This slide presentation features two subject matter experts, Rob Jenkins and Maricel Santos, discussing how to support and motivate adult learners to persist.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: left;"&gt;
&lt;li style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Rob Jenkins is Associate Professor of English as a Second Language at Santa Ana College School of Continuing Education.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: left;"&gt;
&lt;li style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="line-height: 1.231; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Maricel Santos is Associate Professor of English at San Francisco State University.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: left;"&gt;
&lt;li style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;The presenters draw several examples from ESL contexts, and these may easily be adapted for use in ABE/ASE classes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: left;"&gt;
&lt;li style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;The presenters share examples through teaching/learning vignettes. As you listen, watch for the strategies you read about in Unit 1 and which form the basis of the Pre-Course self-assessment you took.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: left;"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;TIP: To hear Rob and Maricel’s narration, be sure to view this PowerPoint presentation in Slideshow mode and turn up the volume on your speakers or headset. You will control the speed of the presentation by pressing “enter” on your keyboard when you are ready to move ahead.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;a href="@@PLUGINFILE@@/MotivatingAdults_ImplementationPPT.ppsx"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Implementing Strategies That Motivate Students to Persist: Stories From Our Classes (PPT)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
