        <title>Post-Viewing Questions</title>
        <content>&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Now that you have watched the video, reflect on the following questions about this teacher’s demonstration of the strategies:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li style="text-align: left;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Which strategies do you think were best demonstrated in this lesson? Choose three from the list provided. (Copy this list below and paste into your &lt;a target="_blank" href="$@JOURNALVIEWBYID*4993@$"&gt;journal&lt;/a&gt; and then indicate which three you think were best demonstrated).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Building Learners’ Self-Efficacy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Setting appropriate goals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Offering feedback to build a growth mindset&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Assisting learners in managing errors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Reframing explanations in ways that motivate persistence (attributions)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Modeling literacy and learning strategies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Using assessments appropriately&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Using and Inspiring Learners’ Interests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Finding value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Providing choice and autonomy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Encouraging collaboration and cooperation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Overcoming Systemic Barriers to Persistence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;Addressing Negative Effects of Stereotypes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
